{"tid":2229201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"踢爆[一名曾在律政司刑事檢控科任職的執業律師回應馬道立聲明]係港共手下的pr寫","createTime":"2020-10-04T08:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T11:40:41.000Z","uid":26770,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8388e6adcfeb1c490377b626a6f25af5a4f03573","tid":2229201,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"各討論區已瘋傳,有興趣可以睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2228925/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2228925/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n點解條友自稱係律師唔係大律師?雖然香港政府都有請事務律師<br />\n但<span class=\"red\">高層全部係bar<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係支那過左國家司法試達到約干要求就係統一叫律師<br />\n所以低學歷大劣五毛係唔知香港制度上有呢個分法</span><br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n搵大公記者扮平民同示威者嘈仲打人<br />\n搵黨報記者接受訪問自稱係受黑暴影響的平民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">現在扮撚埋律政司刑事檢控科任職的執業律師<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">支那五毛戲路仲廣過tvb班垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"00dbfab7658f5c96aca132d27cc3daf1f3ac7bc0","tid":2229201,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"好心la<br />\n<br />\n中共維穩水仲勁過軍費<br />\n雖然個個判判都咩撚都唔做<ins>自己袋一半射落下家</ins><br />\n<br />\n比錢搵個老鬼legal executive寫咪唔會柒lor.....可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c151c21227bd4c88ad7136a08f75b44184bed2","tid":2229201,"uid":286897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f1342bc0ecd864cd5c664c2d0e9abb0a71a4c21","tid":2229201,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又一個冇五毛嘅post"},{"pid":"fd29624fa6f4d8c99621ac0f08b8d8e0f228c974","tid":2229201,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill